snippet.textDisplay: Thanks for the video.  In truth, this stimulus is marginal at best, and most people/families will burn through it exponentially. I don’t need the money, and am considering donating whatever I receive to someone who really needs it.  The democrats, again, have forced their agendas into the stimulus, which neither help impacted families, nor have any relation to this pandemic.  Some will argue that the Republicans include their agendas as well into bills, which is true.....however......this is a stimulus which should be solely targeted on this PANDEMIC......this is an extraordinary circumstance, not business as usual.
